Software/programming language used:
- Python 3.13.7
- ArangoDB 3.11.8
- Arango Python driver : python-arango 8.2.2
- dependencies imported in requirements.txt 

## installing arangodb
- arangodb.com/downloads/
- community edition

## arango python driver 
- pip install python-arango --upgrade

##api/routes.py
- expose all endpoints for hardware and frontend
- change hardware_ip accordingly

##services
- contain all functions ranging from storing, fetching, preprocess etc
- 

